Third, invest in training and enablement. Your sales team needs to understand what intent signals mean, how to respond to different signal patterns, and how to have conversations with prospects showing various levels of intent. Marketing needs to understand how intent data informs content strategy, campaign timing, and audience segmentation. Leadership needs to understand how intent metrics connect to pipeline and revenue outcomes.

